author: Jesse O’Neill
title: Elderly Florida woman drives into outdoor diners, killing one and injuring six
description: An elderly woman behind the wheel was trying to parallel park but accelerated, sending the car barreling into patrons dining outside in Florida.
content:
One person was killed and six others injured when a car plowed into the outdoor dining area of a Florida café on Thursday night, cops said.
